  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">To torture a Levri one must make them a servant. To torture a Puma, you must force them to practice etiquette. To torture a Sparrow, one must simply leave them alone. These Avians are among the most social of all and find maximum satisfaction in interacting with others. Known by all as harmless (even when they are not) and appreciated for their witty and brilliant humor, they are welcome in any environment, where at the same time they go unnoticed and, for their ubiquity, they are missed if absent. They are revelers and rowdy, yet they know how to adapt their conversation to any interlocutor, talking with ease of yeast with bakers, of port taxes with the advisers and of burning gossip with the gentlemen. They are not intimidated by the fame of others, by lineage or religion, often being accused of being irreverent or even blasphemous. Their confidence and ease are however helpful when choosing the ideal approach to take with even the most hostile conversationalists and it is very rare that a Sparrow will resort to arms to resolve even the hottest of arguments.</span> <br style=\"font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:normal;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-size-adjust:auto\" /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Increase in Ability Scores.</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Your <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Dexterity </span>score increases by 2 and your <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Wisdom </span>score increases by 1.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Age.</strong></em> </span>A Pici reaches maturity around the age of 14 <span class=\"fontstyle0\">and is immediately considered independent. They have an average lifespan of around 60 years.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Speed. </strong></em></span></span>Your base speed on the ground is 20 feet, and your <span class=\"fontstyle0\">flight speed is 30 feet.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Size. </strong></em></span>A Sparrow can reach a maximum height of 3 feet, <span class=\"fontstyle0\">and weigh no more than 45 lbs.</span> <span class=\"fontstyle2\">Your size is <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Small</span>.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Sociability.</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You have proficiency in the Persuasion skill.<br /></span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Wild spirit.</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You have expertise in the Survival skill.</span> <br style=\"font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:normal;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-size-adjust:auto\" /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Singer.</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You have expertise in using their voice which is considered to be a musical instrument.</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.ZLta2Wjm3OsgNAk0]{Wings}</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.DO8bJUsTURvkwDVu]{Pecking}</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.9ALHHLuQoSWQRqN4]{Prehensile Legs}</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.3IW3nTEcERwHG4Qg]{Agile}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.ZQMtMEJZdQJ2v63O]{Social Skills}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.K3vkJOhbY84KuNmD]{Maneuvers in Flight}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.2zVRhhfSO8fMZWzt]{Acute Sight}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><em><strong>Instinct of Familia, Harmless (Prey):</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle4\">“I am often not taken seriously.”</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle4\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Instinct of Species, Sociable:</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">“I trust strangers”</span></span></p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
